name: P5S: Persona 5 Strikers
overview: Persona 5 Strikers is an action role-playing game developed by Omega Force and P-Studio and published by Atlus. The game is a crossover between Koei Tecmo's Dynasty Warriors franchise and Atlus' 2016 role-playing game Persona 5, and is set six months after the events of the original Persona 5.
